/*
interruption->

interrupt()-->
use->It is used to interrupt running/executing thread.
interrupt method is work when thread is in sleeping or waiting state( sleep(),wait() )
it throws InterruptedException
public void interrupt();


interrupted() and isInterrupted()-->

interrupted()->It is used to check whether thread is interrupted or not (return boolean value)
isInterrupted()->It is also used to check whether thread is interrupted or not (return boolean value)

difference->

interrupted() clear the status of interruption from true to false if thread is interrupt
isInterrupted() does not clear the status of interruption

interrupted() will change the result
isInterrupted() will not change the result

public static boolean interrupted();
public boolean isInterrupted();

*/
